data.description: Seller's Offering 2/1 INTEREST RATE BUYDOWN or $7,000 for closing costs with accepted terms. The house is located at the end of a peaceful cul-de-sac, offering a secluded and quiet environment. situated on a spacious lot of over 2 acres, the property provides ample space for outdoor activities and privacy. The house has been recently updated with fresh paint and modern lighting fixtures, creating a modern and inviting atmosphere. The backyard is fenced, providing a secure area for children or pets to play freely. A creek runs along the property, adding a serene and natural touch to the surroundings. One of the notable features of this house is that is doesn't have a HOA, giving you more freedom and flexibility in how you use and maintain the property. Despite its peaceful setting, the house is conveniently located just minutes from Columbia, allowing for easy access to amenities and shopping. Additionally, this property allows ownership of chickens to enjoy fresh eggs.
